sg":"<blockquote>你要諗下間公司做乜有錢都唔搵要封殺你個人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講啦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ad9c363d5a99e8b1099f9b8b2e50e3a0e7a4d8","tid":59314,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:19:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你要諗下間公司做乜有錢都唔搵要封殺你個人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講啦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果能年係無錯既 間公司點會咁大仇口有錢都唔賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重要係最紅果期d錢唔使搵都自己會湧埋黎果陣先封殺人<br />\n<br />\n同埋真係咁理直氣壯既會無人出黎幫你出頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbecky搞人老公都成村老屎忽出黎幫佢講野啦"},{"pid":"3b67b408480efbe9f412bd22592ed6ec5c6f0682","tid":59314,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:20:43.000Z","msg":"抵死啦"},{"pid":"288afa420dc93c66581f41a9bb839a07f0bcfa3d","tid":59314,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:24:43.000Z","msg":"你呢個唔係答案喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終都係講唔出到底能年有咩可恨之處<br />\n如果係佢待人接物有問題扮大牌，或者私生活唔檢點<br />\n相信班狗仔咁多年以來都一早查到出嚟<br />\n<br />\n其實都可以係<br />\n1，有同公司嘅大牌女明星唔鍾意佢，威脅捧佢就走<br />\n2，有啲老闆係好迷信嘅，覺得捧能年會厄運<br />\n3，除咗小海女嘅角色啱佢外，其實能年實力欠奉<br />\n<br />\n冇証據，根本就任你up架姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bfc443c253f0c434cffd9b5afb6644f25e34cc","tid":59314,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:25:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你要諗下間公司做乜有錢都唔搵要封殺你個人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講啦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果能年係無錯既 間公司點會咁大仇口有錢都唔賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" 